<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        nav {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        nav a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: #007BFF;
        }
        section {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .skills, .projects, .experience, .education {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .contact {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .contact p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1><%= locals.name %></h1>
        <p>Web Developer & Designer</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
        <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="#education">Education</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Hello! I'm <%=locals.name%>, a passionate web developer. I love coding and am always eager to learn new technologies and improve my skills.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="skills" class="skills">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <p>HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Node.js, Express, MongoDB,Responsive Web Design</p>
    </section>

    <section id="projects" class="projects">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <p><strong>Project 1:</strong> Portfolio Website - A personal portfolio website to showcase my skills and projects.</p>
        <p><strong>Project 2:</strong> Employee Info Website - A website where you can track over your employee.</p>
        <p><strong>Project 3:</strong> KnowYourWorld Website - A website where you can find about the whole world.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="education" class="education">
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <p><strong><%= locals.university %><br></strong> - B.Voc(Web Designing) (2022-2025)</p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <h2>Contact Me</h2>
        <p>Email: <%= locals.email %></p>
        <p>Phone(Fictional): +123-456-7890</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 <%=locals.name%>. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
